{"TopicId":189282,"ForumId":29,"TopicTitle":"[SOLVED] [1.8] what\u0026#039;s the update for Input.GetKeyUp(KeyCode)","CreatedByName":"Xyphos","CreatedById":139010,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-10-25T10:17:28Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Xyphos","CreatedById":139010,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-10-25T10:17:28Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nthe 1.8 update transitioned to a new version of Unity which broke most of the mods, and I\u0027ve updated all but one of mine;\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI can\u0027t figure out the new keyboard input system, the old system was Input.GetKeyUp(Keycode) and now it\u0027s showing errors\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222019-10-26T06:54:54Z\u0022 title=\u002210/26/2019 06:54  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00224 yr\u0022\u003EOctober 26, 2019\u003C/time\u003E by Xyphos\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Xyphos","CreatedById":139010,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-10-26T00:49:59Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAnd found my answer; they changed it from Input.GetKeyUp(KeyCode) to ExtendedInput.GetKeyUp(KeyCode)\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\na minor edit, but what a pain changing it.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"linuxgurugamer","CreatedById":129964,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-11-22T00:13:59Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223694877\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022189282\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221572050999\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022139010\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Xyphos\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nOn 10/25/2019 at 8:49 PM, Xyphos said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAnd found my answer; they changed it from Input.GetKeyUp(KeyCode) to ExtendedInput.GetKeyUp(KeyCode)\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\na minor edit, but what a pain changing it.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThat came when they added localization to the game.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}